<span class="comment"><font color=#000000>SOAP - Remote procedure calls (maybe) that use web frameworks and XML when I all really wanted was to know the latest user setting.<p>CORBA - Remote procedure calls (maybe) for object-oriented programmers who can't agree which language to use, but are expected to agree on how to represent it.<p>Design Patterns - What to use when your language isn't up for the task.</font></span><p><font size=1><font color=#f6f6ef>-----</font></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table border=0><tr><td><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/s.gif" height=1 width=40></td><td valign=top><center><a id=up_2127764 href="vote?for=2127764&dir=up&whence=%2f%78%3f%66%6e%69%64%3d%55%74%53%79%48%41%33%53%76%33"><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/grayarrow.gif" border=0 vspace=3 hspace=2></a><span id=down_2127764></span></center></td><td class="default"><div style="margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:-10px; "><span class="comhead"><a href="user?id=br1">br1</a> 379 days ago  | <a href="item?id=2127764">link</a></span></div><br>
